attributes.review:
When I first opened the app, it said the app was down because, and I quote, “Trump was taking a poop.” 🤔🤔💩I immediately left, and waited a few hours to get back in. I opened the app, and waited over 30 MINUTES ⏰FOR THE LOADING SCREEN TO 🛑 . Then, there were tons of ads everywhere I clicked. And then the most disgusting ad of all showed up: A PORN AD. 😣😣😱😱 I was horrified! I almost threw my phone in disgust. I took a deep breath and decided to give it one last shot. This time, my brother 👫 decided to watch with me. Here’s where it gets horrifying 😮😮😮😨😨😨😰😰😰. I got in, after another 40 MINUTES, and then the app said it was again unavailable. Its reason? “On the way to egg my house.” WHAT IS THAT, TRUMP?! On my brother’s phone, it said the app was unavailable and they told him to “kick rocks.” 
Against my better judgement 😣 I came back. I realized I had forgotten to delete the app 😠 . I was just about to delete it when I realized they had sent me an email 📧 and let me know they had updated it and it was much better ☺️.  So I gave it a try. I had to wait 15 minutes for the loading screen to go away 🙄 and went I finally got in, I saw a strange button 🤔 and I clicked on it 😏. It said, spin the wheel for a mystery outcome. So, I spun it and my result was a fire emoji. 🔥 I was confused 🤷‍♀️ but I carried on exploring until this happened 😭 I went to feed my Komodo 🐉 , until I realized his cage was on 🔥 ! I swear, I saw the secret service 👮‍♀️ running away from my farm. I am positive 👍 I’m voting for Biden in november.
